@node "History" "History"

                             History
                            =========

      This Util started as an afternoon hack as most utils do..
      I just wanted to improve all the other comment doors out
      there, as I thought they were to complex to install and
      configure.

            V 0.8ß ----  Nothing worked as it should

            V 0.9ß ----  It worked!!  sometimes =(

            V 1.0ß ----  Everything worked as it should =)

            V 1.1  ----  Added separate config file
@endnode

@node "Installation" "Installation"

                           Installation
                          ==============

    The installation is farely easy!......

    Just copy the E_comment.rexx and the E_comment.config to the
    DOORS: directory on your system.

    This door should be run in Exclusive mode as it does not check
    internally if it is used by two nodes at the same time.
@endnode

@node "Config" "Configuring E_comment"

                               Config
                              ========

    This will teach you to config the E_comment for your
    personal system. Just follow the instructions step by
    step and there should be no problems.

    Before you edit the config file it should look like this:

    John Doe
    SysOp, The one you all admire.. =)
    Don Smith
    CoSysOp, Grafix
    James Smith
    CoSysOp, Amiga Freak...
    Robert Smith
    CoSysOp, Filevalidation

    The first line is the username of the person, the second
    the description of him, The third is the second username
    and so on......

    You can enter as many entries as there is room for on a
    screen. Just make sure that you enter the username
    correctly or the door wont function properly.
@endnode

